Name: Average resolution time following 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' activities in cases with 'Accepted + Wait - User' preceding it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Longest duration from 'Completed + In Call' to case closure
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Shortest duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases with high impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' activities across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' after case start
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' before case closure
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average duration from 'Completed + In Call' to the next activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Closed' in the fastest resolved cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Duration from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Closed' in the slowest resolved cases
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Accepted + Assigned' in the process flow
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases with 'Medium' impact versus 'High' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases ending with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' activities in cases exceeding average case duration
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time to 'Completed + In Call' from case initiation
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration variance of 'Completed + In Call' across different organization countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total count of 'Completed + In Call' activities preceding 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
